overview.en: BBO is a professional financial transaction platform in the field of global blockchain, which provides financial services for blockchain and is committed to building a new blockchain technology financial platform. Making use of blockchain technology to build a safe and reliable blockchain financial service ecological platform for the majority of users, committed to eliminating transaction barriers, improving transaction efficiency and promoting economic development
overview.zh: BBO 是全球区块链领域专业金融理财交易平台，为区块链提供金融服务，致力于打造新兴的区块链技术金融平台。利用区块链技术为广大用户打造安全可靠的区块链金融服务生态平台，致力于消除交易壁垒，提升交易效率，促进经济发展
